{"prompt": "Generate a website for a podcasting network. The website should be bold and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Crimson Waves Network</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #c0392b;\n            --secondary-color: #e74c3c;\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item {\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n            padding: 25px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--brand-color);\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 3px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            border-top: 5px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            section h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Crimson Waves Network</h1>\n            <p>Where bold ideas make waves.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.7;\">\n                Crimson Waves Network is a premier podcasting hub dedicated to bringing you the most captivating and thought-provoking audio content. We curate a diverse range of shows that explore culture, technology, true crime, and beyond, all delivered with passion and a commitment to quality. Dive into a world of sound and join our growing community.\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"podcasts\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Featured Podcasts</h2>\n            <div class=\"podcast-grid\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/c0392b/ffffff?text=Podcast+1\" alt=\"Podcast Cover 1\">\n                    <h3>The Echo Chamber</h3>\n                    <p>Exploring the latest in digital culture and its impact on society.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Listen Now</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e74c3c/ffffff?text=Podcast+2\" alt=\"Podcast Cover 2\">\n                    <h3>Crimson Truths</h3>\n                    <p>Unpacking complex historical events with fresh perspectives.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Listen Now</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/c0392b/ffffff?text=Podcast+3\" alt=\"Podcast Cover 3\">\n                    <h3>Velocity Talks</h3>\n                    <p>Interviews with innovators shaping the future of technology.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Listen Now</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e74c3c/ffffff?text=Podcast+4\" alt=\"Podcast Cover 4\">\n                    <h3>Midnight Mysteries</h3>\n                    <p>Investigating unsolved cases and chilling tales from the dark.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Listen Now</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Join the Conversation</h2>\n            <p>Follow us on social media and subscribe to our newsletter to stay updated on new episodes and network news.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Subscribe</a>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\" style=\"background-color: #333; border-color: #555;\">Follow Us</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Crimson Waves Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic smooth scrolling for anchor links\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}